## STEP-BY-STEP: MIGRATE ANY PAGE

1. Check apa tables diperlukan oleh page tu
2. Create table di Supabase kalau belum ada
3. Insert data dari data.json kalau perlu
4. Tambah Supabase SDK dalam HTML page (3 script tags sebelum api.js)
5. Push ke GitHub dengan version yang betul
6. Test page berfungsi

### Supabase SDK Script Tags (tambah SEBELUM api.js)
```html
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
<script src="PATH/shared/js/supabase-config.js"></script>
<script src="PATH/shared/js/api.js"></script>
```

PATH varies by depth:
- index.html: shared/js/...
- account/pages/login/: ../../../shared/js/...
- customer/pages/dashboard/: ../../../shared/js/...
- admin/pages/dashboard/: ../../../shared/js/...
- customer/pages/car-details/booking/payment/: ../../../../../shared/js/...

