## COMMON BUGS & FIXES

### Logout redirect loop
Login page auto-redirect balik ke dashboard.
Fix: Only check hash #access_token
```javascript
var hash = window.location.hash;
if (!hash || !hash.includes('access_token')) return;
```

### Column mismatch on insert
Fix: Check columns dulu: SELECT column_name FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_name = 'x';

### Supabase SDK not loaded
Fix: Tambah 2 script sebelum api.js

### Google provider not enabled
Fix: Use lowercase keys: external_google_enabled, external_google_client_id, external_google_secret

### Email verification blocking
Fix: Set mailer_autoconfirm: true

